    "Our method is implemented with PyTorch and trained on a server with eight NVIDIA H800 GPUs.",
    "All attack methods are limited to a maximum number of searches N m = 50, with unsuccessful jailbreaks beyond this threshold deemed failures.",
    "We evaluate across typical LLMs including Vicuna-7B/13B/33B (Chiang et al., 2023), Llama3-8B-Instruct (Grattafiori et al., 2024), and Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.3 foot_6.",
    "We set T r = {I, I ′ m, As, Sorry} (Yu et al., 2023; Lin et al., 2024).",
    "We train the LLMs with Open-RLHF (Hu et al., 2024))."
  ],
